text: Rogerick Green (born December 15, 1969) is a former American football defensive back. He played for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers in 1992 and 1994 and for the Jacksonville Jaguars in 1995. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:American football defensive backs Category:Kansas State Wildcats football players Category:Tampa Bay Buccaneers players Category:Jacksonville Jaguars players
